{"tid":1657518,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"罷鷲其實真係超級神獸來架","createTime":"2019-10-16T06:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T07:46:25.000Z","uid":272200,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3772b9acca3f36894d991eeda06cc8ae1850c1d4","tid":1657518,"uid":272200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"TL;DR<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">罷鷲三個月就已經可以令餐飲業大洗牌，唔係講笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解：<br />\n我做左小小研究：平均來講，香港食店支出大約係咁：<br />\n40%-60%：舖租<br />\n20%-25%：食材<br />\n20%-25%：人工<br />\n10%：雜項<br />\n基本上係梗既，無得點郁。<br />\n<br />\n而重點係，其實香港飲食業係微利行業，每間食店，不論大小，Net profit margin 其實都只是10%之內，即是一間每月盈業額60萬既食店，老闆其實只係賺緊六萬左右。<br />\n<br />\n係香港，黃絲佔總人口近七八成。我當肯罷鷲的黃絲有一半，能持續每天執行的又只有一半好了。咁，香港既藍店就會少左人口中 80%x0.5x0.5 = 20% 帶來既盈業額。<br />\n<br />\n即係話，我當食店10% profit margin:<br />\n盈業額60萬既藍絲食店，少左20%生意，變成50萬，<span style=\"color: red;\">老闆收入就由賺6萬，變成負4萬！</span><br />\n相反，盈業額60萬既黃絲食店，多左20%人口既生意，藍店蝕幾多就佢地賺番哂，<span style=\"color: gold;\">老闆收入絕對倍增！</span><br />\n<br />\n最重要係，數學上只有盈利能力超過20%既藍店先至唔會蝕，但係飲食業絕對少有！<br />\n(政府統計2017年飲食業profit margin約為5.5%)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B10800142017AN17B0100.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FB10800142017AN17B0100.pdf&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVkZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=38eb2e31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/B10800142017AN17B0100.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n所以結論不輪大小食店，間間都會因為罷鷲而由大受影響，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一係執笠（藍店）</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一係大肆擴充（黃店）</span></span>"},{"pid":"70925681b85e0af2e751d22a018ac1055e69358b","tid":1657518,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC4rszp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC4rszp.jpg&h=a54a4986&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d368a8ddfb9a5660b4a131017a4593672649d559","tid":1657518,"uid":152976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:41:23.000Z","msg":"唔好理 keep半年再講成效 做左先算"},{"pid":"852ef354b6bce1a3eaeaf909542a46f9bc3a6f64","tid":1657518,"uid":118120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"兩大神獸<br />\n文有罷鷲 , 武有獅鳥"},{"pid":"982c93fb70699b844ba40793974c2210670ee770","tid":1657518,"uid":198932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d368a8ddfb9a5660b4a131017a4593672649d559","tid":1657518,"uid":152976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:41:23.000Z","msg":"唔好理 keep半年再講成效 做左先算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"需要全面擴展黃藍list<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b32004c2f058180dd559c1d4096713a60cabbf0","tid":1657518,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"852ef354b6bce1a3eaeaf909542a46f9bc3a6f64","tid":1657518,"uid":118120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"兩大神獸<br />\n文有罷鷲 , 武有獅鳥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f656eaa1e1955102883d7f1c680e76a7d4820e3","tid":1657518,"uid":59679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"852ef354b6bce1a3eaeaf909542a46f9bc3a6f64","tid":1657518,"uid":118120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"兩大神獸<br />\n文有罷鷲 , 武有獅鳥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:33:10.000Z","msg":"正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3322334ebadc5165218dd9f786afd2851f1aadc","tid":1657518,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:3